{"tid":1939303,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劃時代經典科幻動畫亞基拉下個月上畫","createTime":"2020-03-23T05:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T18:55:49.000Z","uid":5218,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"69e9a9523c4d2eb4c1f6647ec6ab32893c7da80a","tid":1939303,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"但唔知香港上既係咪 4k 版本呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大友克洋的劃時代漫畫成就劃時代動畫片，當年日本公映墟陷程度，比美《星球大戰》，動畫迷選十大百大，每次都躋身前列。1988年東京離奇大爆炸，2019年新東京都人心莽撞，法紀蕩搖，飆車少年黨遇上秘密警察捉拿埃斯帕 Akira，當年災難背後的陰謀陸續顯現，悲情少年也成為預言中危機的本身。動作及科技視覺走在最前，但亦緊密呼應科幻傳統，延伸自己的《Fireball》，也向橫山光輝的《鐵人28號》挪用角色盡情致敬，美術視覺遙呼費列茲朗的《大都會》，它自為典範後，又繼續影響《22世紀殺人網路》、《新世紀福音戰士》《潛行兇間》、《蝙蝠俠&mdash;黑夜之神》等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/202003/FB_IMG_1584700428608_1584781032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F202003%2FFB_IMG_1584700428608_1584781032.jpg&h=5412384d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9553fe5a3b4e70b69d6eba4466956af2be233d54","tid":1939303,"uid":38566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"預言東京奧運"},{"pid":"1ca4b442cdc9e400f7c7c8f9276ac5a86c4877f6","tid":1939303,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"入唔入戲院睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一邊中癈炎一邊睇"},{"pid":"9ec84f86d41277ff4ba20d59e6de5670316a0388","tid":1939303,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca4b442cdc9e400f7c7c8f9276ac5a86c4877f6","tid":1939303,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"入唔入戲院睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一邊中癈炎一邊睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"吹緊風關戲院,睇來唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /